+        // [GIVEN] General Journal with two lines in Currency EUR:
+        // [GIVEN] Line1: Amount = 480 EUR, Amount (LCY) = 5266.67, "Automatic Account Group" = "AAG"
+        // [GIVEN] Line2: Amount = -480 EUR, Amount (LCY) = -5266.67 (balancing line)
